{"tid":104953,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"3000 budget 內父母用傻瓜機","createTime":"2017-02-02T13:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T13:15:02.000Z","uid":81766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"134c55f5339087fc1fc72f9b7e22b7047ce8e3ef","tid":104953,"uid":81766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"自己本身對影相無咩研究，最近父母退休不停去旅行，想買番部傻瓜機比佢地旁身。<br />\n<br />\n佢地完全無攝影既知識，剩係識用auto對焦，禁制，想問3000 畢直各位巴絲有咩推介？<br />\n<br />\n影得正正常常對人像清晰就可以，唔該晒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我有望過下最近相機，<br />\nSony DSC-HX90V<br />\nFuji X30<br />\n<br />\n但都有過畢直，有無其他好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85047cac1c529911fdb8a49992c732c886793b8","tid":104953,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T13:53:30.000Z","msg":"即影即有啱哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adc3f24e9be608d6f9068c00a5b3d7779d9493b","tid":104953,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即影即有啱哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsonar sx-70 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9766223afead968b0869954cb416178680b2bd61","tid":104953,"uid":7955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:12:46.000Z","msg":"呢個預算，買部電話算啦　<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c157cae02d0499cc66c1b8c6a7673e0144ba613","tid":104953,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:14:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e695149c6bfff0e4a10aa203bdef568d151a7b25","tid":104953,"uid":81766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T16:25:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常死老野好少周圍去旅行，因為驚舟車勞頓辛苦，同埋死老野個膀胱容積細，忍唔到尿，加上慳儉，唔願駛錢<br />\n<br />\n我建議買部電話影相或者DC仔算<br />\n<br />\nSony DSC-HX90V<br />\nFuji X30<br />\n<br />\n我上<a href=\"http://price.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprice.com.hk&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=5150bcb8\" target=\"_blank\">http://price.com.hk</a>睇，第一部機好過第二部機，像素高d，光學變焦係30x，第二部機冇寫到有幾倍光學變焦，所以我當係零<br />\n<br />\n第一部機平d，輕d，體積（尺寸）又細d，點睇都係第一部機好</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n佢地都有電話，但又想有部dc仔旁下身咁，買完我自己都用得既又無所謂，唔係我想要3000畢直，不過近期dc仔d價值直奔上天空，加多幾千畢直可以玩單反添喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0896b0d2ac666812738bf738cdc9df6ec91d20d8","tid":104953,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T16:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常死老野好少周圍去旅行，因為驚舟車勞頓辛苦，同埋死老野個膀胱容積細，忍唔到尿，加上慳儉，唔願駛錢<br />\n<br />\n我建議買部電話影相或者DC仔算<br />\n<br />\nSony DSC-HX90V<br />\nFuji X30<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://我上price.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%88%91%E4%B8%8Aprice.com.hk&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a2a5e382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">我上price.com.hk</a>睇，第一部機好過第二部機，像素高d，光學變焦係30x，第二部機冇寫到有幾倍光學變焦，所以我當係零<br />\n<br />\n第一部機平d，輕d，體積（尺寸）又細d，點睇都係第一部機好</blockquote><br />\n無撚病嘛？<br />\n上Price睇spec之餘仲要當x30無變焦"},{"pid":"1f9626a6e78d7699c76346d1f3ef18f195baf249","tid":104953,"uid":41037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T16:51:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adbbfe36359384f30a9460791dd238d7c74a9d7d","tid":104953,"uid":36174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T16:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>通常死老野好少周圍去旅行，因為驚舟車勞頓辛苦，同埋死老野個膀胱容積細，忍唔到尿，加上慳儉，唔願駛錢<br />\n<br />\n我建議買部電話影相或者DC仔算<br />\n<br />\nSony DSC-HX90V<br />\nFuji X30<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://我上price.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%88%91%E4%B8%8Aprice.com.hk&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a2a5e382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">我上price.com.hk</a>睇，第一部機好過第二部機，像素高d，光學變焦係30x，第二部機冇寫到有幾倍光學變焦，所以我當係零<br 